1. Clicking the Up Arrow (⬆) should move the selection to the previous message one by one, without jumping multiple messages at once.
2. Clicking the Down Arrow (⬇) should move the selection to the next message one by one.
3. The navigation should be smooth and responsive.
4. When at the first message, the Up Arrow (⬆) should be disabled.
5. When at the latest message, the Down Arrow (⬇) should be disabled.
6. The currently selected message should be highlighted or indicated properly.
